### 48. OCCELUS (OR OCELLUS) OF LUCANIA

<span class="smallcaps">Occelus</span> (or <span
class="smallcaps">Ocellus</span>) of <span
class="smallcaps">Lucania</span>: date uncertain.

Titles of several works were ascribed to him; but passages from a
treatise *On the Nature of the Whole* are thought to be a forgery.

